From: Nickel Browser Team <team@nickel-browser.org>
Date: Thu, 01 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Nickel Browser: Tor Private Tab Integration

This patch integrates the official Tor binary for private tab functionality.
Routes tab traffic through Tor network with zero leaks.

